@SupraDarky
Wily Stage 1/2 is a great tune.. heck, MM2 in general has a great soundtrack. Just irks me a little that many other songs in the series are overlooked in favor of MM2.. like many of the songs from MM5 (Charge Man, Napalm Man, and Stone Man to name three). Skull Man and DIve Man from MM4 are other examples. Oh well.. :)

Glad you have some of the tunes from the other games on your list, including the aforementioned Skull Man.
